<i>Posted by Xiao on 11-27-2001 09:09 PM:</i>

<p><b> 
</b></p>

<p>As far as I know, Bris knew that Mythic considered it a bug.  He just happens to disagree with that assessment.  I can see his point, in that it's balanced by draining endurance when you change chants - this limits the combat styles you can do and your ability to flee battle.  It also makes a chant-heavy pally more useful than they would be otherwise, able to only do one of 3 (?) chants as they are.<!-- BEGIN TEMPLATE: postbit_signature -->
