<br />
Mercs and Pallies can now both solo yellows, it's just that pallies won't end up at full life and mercs at half life any more.<br />
<br />
Of course, this is all coming from a low level gimp.  I'm sure there are other high level concerns that I can't possibly comprehend.<!-- BEGIN TEMPLATE: postbit_signature -->
