<i>Posted by Gakkenfeld on 11-28-2001 03:35 PM:</i>

<p><b> 
</b></p>

<p>Change on Test:<b><br />
<br />
Thank you for the feedback. The team reconsidered the choice based on your comments about endurance loss being a major factor, and paladins will be able to keep "twisting" their songs if they choose that play style as opposed to combat styles. <br />
<br />
Please keep in mind, however, that "stacking" two different heals IS a bug and will be corrected eventually. Those two songs are not supposed to stack, and it does cause some imbalance. <br />
<br />
This is why we have a test server, guys. Not everything on test will make it to the live servers! Thanks again for the input - I especially want to thank a few people who sent email. They were very calm and non-confrontational, and I was able to take it all to the producer. </b><!-- BEGIN TEMPLATE: postbit_signature -->
